WEBVTT

00:00:00.310 --> 00:00:04.326
Let's begin with a story.

00:00:04.326 --> 00:00:06.277
Once upon a time --

00:00:06.277 --> 00:00:09.343
well actually less than two years ago --

00:00:09.343 --> 00:00:12.376
in a kingdom not so very far away,

00:00:12.376 --> 00:00:14.127
there was a man

00:00:14.127 --> 00:00:15.994
who traveled many miles

00:00:15.994 --> 00:00:19.576
to come to work at the jewel in the kingdom's crown --

00:00:19.576 --> 00:00:22.160
an internationally famous company.

00:00:22.160 --> 00:00:25.278
Let's call it Island Networks.

00:00:25.278 --> 00:00:28.126
Now this kingdom had many resources

00:00:28.126 --> 00:00:30.343
and mighty ambitions,